title: Stylight
brief: This group is about building the local tech community in Munich. We like to bring people together and create events like with our Tech Frühstück where members of our community can gather to show the cool things they've been working on.

title: ACM Student Club
brief: The Munich Student Chapter was founded in 2015. The chapter is established to primarily serve the wide scope of ACM which is advancing computing as a science and profession by supporting and training the next generation of computer scientists.

title: Nerds4Refugees
brief: Nerds4refugees is a group of individuals with an affinity to technology, responding to the current refugee crisis in Germany, through offering IT related skills and experience.
